lical%2C+Theological%2C+and+Ecclesiastical+Literature%2C+Volume+11&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pages=555&amp;rft.pub=Harper+%26+Brothers&amp;rft.date=1889&amp;rft.aulast=McClintock&amp;rft.aufirst=John&amp;rft.au=James+Strong&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2F%3Fid%3DTHZPAAAAYAAJ%26pg%3DPA555%26lpg%3DPA555%26dq%3Dfran%25C3%25A7ois%2Bbonivard%2Bturin%2B1510%23v%3Donepage%26q%3Dfran%25C3%25A7ois%2520bonivard%2520turin%25201510%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFran%C3%A7ois+Bonivard\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Chr-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Chr_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Chr_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Bacon, Leonard Woolsey (April 1895). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/?id=LOXbAAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PA316&amp;lpg=PA316&amp;dq=bonivard+chaponniere#v=onepage&amp;q=bonivard%20chaponniere&amp;f=false\">\"The Real Prisoner of Chillon: A Curious Episode in Ecclesiastical History\"</a>. <i>Christian Literature</i>. England: Lightning Source. <b>12</b> (6): 316. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-278-82967-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1-278-82967-9\">1-278-82967-9</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Christian+Literature&amp;rft.atitle=The+Real+Prisoner+of+Chillon%3A+A+Curious+Episode+in+Ecclesiastical+History&amp;rft.volume=12&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=316&amp;rft.date=1895-04&amp;rft.isbn=1-278-82967-9&amp;rft.aulast=Bacon&amp;rft.aufirst=Leonard+Woolsey&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2F%3Fid%3DLOXbAAAAMAAJ%26pg%3DPA316%26lpg%3DPA316%26dq%3Dbonivard%2Bchaponnier